Package: gencor
Type: Package
Title: Generate Customized Correlation Matrices
Version: 1.0.0
Depends:
    base,
Author: Helgem de Souza Ribeiro Martins[aut, cre], Anderson Ribeiro Duarte[aut]
Maintainer: Helgem de Souza Ribeiro Martins <helgem.souza@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a function that generates customized correlation matrix based on 
    limit values and proportions for intervals composed by its limits. Can also generate 
    random correlation matrices, matrices with low, medium and high correlations, which 
    low, medium and high thresholds are user-defined.
